    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, bash your<strong> lemongrass </strong>with a <strong>rolling pin</strong>, remove the <strong>tough outer layer[s] </strong>and<strong> </strong>set aside for later</p><p>Chop the<strong> softer inner core[s]</strong> roughly</p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong> roughly</p><p>Peel and roughly chop your <strong>ginger</strong>, <strong>garlic </strong>and<strong> shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Slice <strong>half </strong>of your <strong>red chilli</strong> into rounds and roughly chop the rest</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1612273795905-x200.jpg",
