    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the tofu<strong> </strong>is golden and crisp, transfer it to a plate<strong> </strong>and return the pan to a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>Thai-style curry paste</strong> and cook for 2 min until fragrant</p><p>Meanwhile, dissolve your<strong> creamed coconut</strong> in 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[250ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[300ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>with the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lime[s] </strong>and a pinch of<strong> sugar </strong>– this is your<strong> coconut stock</strong></p>",
