            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>coconut stock</strong> to the pan and cook for 2-3 min further until the sauce has thickened</p><p>Add the <strong>crispy tofu </strong>and <strong>roasted butternut squash & pepper</strong> to the pan then gently mix it all together – this is your <strong>Thai-style tofu & butternut squash curry</strong></p><p>Slice the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>lime </strong>into wedges</p>",
