    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Thai-style tofu & butternut squash curry</strong> over the <strong>sticky</strong> <strong>lemongrass rice</strong></p><p>Top with the <strong>chill rounds</strong> (not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) and a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
